These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, siglo, tiparillo
House: craftsman, tower, colonial
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, car
City: edinburgh, san-francisco, new-york
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person traveling to new-york is the mechanic##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person driving the car and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the designer is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 6. the colonial house is the person driving the tram##1
 7. the colonial house is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the designer##1
10. the tower house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Cigar          | siglo       | tiparillo    | oliveros         |
| House         | tower    | colonial  | craftsman        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Transport   | skateboard     | tram  | car       |
| City         | edinburgh     | san-francisco | new-york |

