.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, hiking
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, davidoff, blend
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, rock
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, brown, chestnut
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, journalist, teacher
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the teacher is the person who likes brown##1
 2. the teacher is the blend-smoker##1
 3. the blend-smoker is on the right of the manager##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is chess##2
 5. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the swisher-smoker##1
 9. the blend-smoker is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the teacher is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Hobby      | chess   | hiking    | filmmaking         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Cigar   | swisher  | blend  | davidoff     |
