3 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, bridge
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, russian
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, lavender, turquise
 1. the person eating kale is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the russian is the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the person drinking coffee is the person eating peas##1
 4. the person drinking water is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is between the indian and the person playing bridge##2
 8. the indian is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the indian is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Food          | peas      | kale      | cabbage      |
| Flower         | marigold   | bellflower | orchid |
