 1. the fan of reggae is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is in the middle##1
 3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the craftsman house is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the wooden house is between the person who's birthday is in june and the fonseca-smoker##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the craftsman house##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the craftsman house is the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | june | may      | august      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Cigar   | dannemann  | dunhill     | fonseca |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Music-Genre         | jazz    | reggae | funk   |
| House     | colonial        | wooden        | craftsman   |

