.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk
House: modern, victorian, tower
There are 3 different nationalities: german, nigerian, italian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bongani, chaman
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
City: nizza, new-york, prague
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the tower house##1
3. the victorian house is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching epic movies and the bongani-smoker##2
5. the tower house is between the chaman-smoker and the italian##2
6. the nigerian is on the right of the tower house##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | juice      | milk       |
| House          | victorian      | tower    | modern   |
| Nationality         | italian    | german     | nigerian     |
| Cigar           | bongani    | aristoff | chaman   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | mystery    | epic       |
| Sport         | water-polo | rugby      | surfing    |
| City     | new-york       | nizza | prague |

