.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta
City: london, new-york, paris
House: futuristic, gothic-revival, farmhouse
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, siglo, alhambra
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, reggae
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, snowboarding
3 different games are played: poker, billiard, backgammon
1. the person playing billiard is the gothic-revival house##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is between the person drinking fanta and the futuristic house##2
6. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the person playing poker is the alhambra-smoker##1
9. the futuristic house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | fanta       | coffee     | cola         |
| City          | london     | new-york      | paris     |
| House         | gothic-revival | farmhouse    | futuristic      |
| Cigar   | fonseca   | siglo | alhambra    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | reggae     | electronic   |
| Sport         | cricket     | ice-hockey | snowboarding |
| Game     | billiard     | backgammon       | poker    |

