.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, tea
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, card-games, dancing
House: tower, farmhouse, palace
3 different games are played: poker, backgammon, billiard
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, salsa, house
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person driving the roller is the fan of r&b##1
3. the tower house is between the person drinking tea and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the fan of house##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the farmhouse house is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the person playing backgammon is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | milk       | tea      |
| Hobby          | hiking   | dancing   | card-games  |
| House           | farmhouse  | tower | palace    |
| Game   | poker   | backgammon     | billiard  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog        | hedgehog |
| Music-Genre         | salsa | r&b   | house  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 